# Workspace Scope

**Declare scope at task start:** `mobile` | `web` | `shared` | `cross-cutting`

## Path map

| Scope | Paths | Docs |
|-------|-------|------|
| **Mobile** | `mobile/src/**` | `docs/specs/monetization/paywall.md`, `docs/specs/gameplay/` |
| **Web** | `web/editor-app/**` | `docs/web/`, `docs/monetization/CONSTRUCTOR_IMPL_PLAN.md` |
| **Shared** | `supabase/**`, `shared/**`, `docs/monetization/` | Domain + schema |
| **Cross-cutting** | monetization, entities, analytics | `docs/_meta/discrepancy-matrix.md` |

## Rules

| File | Scope |
|------|-------|
| `documentation.mdc` | Doc system (always) |
| `common.mdc` | Code style, spec contract, no-legacy, comments |
| `mobile.mdc` | `mobile/**` |
| `web.mdc` | `web/**` |

## Cross-cutting checklist

Monetization / gameplay entity changes:

1. `docs/specs/` or `docs/monetization/`
2. `supabase/migrations/` if schema
3. `mobile/src/` if player behavior
4. `web/editor-app/` if author UI

Open **Limerence-Workspace** as Cursor root.
